   <p>This table shows, that in the district schools, in which German instruction is now given, the number of pupils has risen from, 3,359 to 3,724 of whom 1,525 are <pb facs="5418474_1_0804.jpg" n="3"/>of her German descent, while 2,199 are not Germans.</p>
   <p>German instruction was a subject, of great interest an every school and the woman teachers are responsible for the enthusiasm which the students have for the German language.</p>
